{"tid":611781,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱表完白 求屌醒","createTime":"2018-03-31T11:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T07:13:46.000Z","uid":40145,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a34de34dc241687f39a0bd0817686e72cc88b0","tid":611781,"uid":40145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:23:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，條女就要返外國讀書啦，咁我就早幾日約咗佢出街，<span style=\"color: red;\">我</span>覺得好好feel，於是諗住今日表白。<br />\n咁我就諗住今日等佢揾完fd就出去揾佢送佢返屋企再講啦，點知佢話唔好啦，未執行李。老實講我都知冇好結果啦 不過我覺得點都要試，於是我wtsapp咗佢 同佢講完就俾佢拒絕咗。佢話唔想拍拖，我話如果你都中意我點解唔可以俾個機會我？之後佢就話諗下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我之所以會表白係因為我知佢都中意我 佢1月嘅時候講過 之後係外國又會日日講電話啦 返到黎又約到諗住實得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知現實係殘酷嘅<br />\n我真係好中意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同fd講完佢就話你都表咗3次白啦 點解仲要留戀 大佬 你話放低就放低咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個女仔我追咗年半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亦係最中意個個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  究竟我應該放手定等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:我覺得佢係怕long d同真係唔想拍拖<br />\n    衰d咁諗:可能佢一開賽話佢都中意我只係唔想hurt我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢同我d fd講又話有中意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n求屌醒"},{"pid":"68f5b4815c384f2a0e3b2fdfdff2e956cec04233","tid":611781,"uid":40145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:23:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ca2c16139ec0cfba8753b6b3ae59e28425c9d1","tid":611781,"uid":87466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T11:24:36.000Z","msg":"醒下啦，冇機會架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c927375d18a1c0a00e0bc435f4b36434ba48e547","tid":611781,"uid":155949,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T1